FANTASTIC FUNDRAISER GETS OFF TO A SIZZLING START
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Saturday evening saw sparks flying, quite literally, from the heels
    of the Crossway Pregnancy Crisis Centre team. Accompanied by ten
    other brave participants, they removed their shoes and socks,
    rolled up their trousers, and walked barefoot across a path
    of red-hot burning coals, raising an incredible &pound;2,791 for
    the charity.

